---

import profile from "../assets/images/willow-bud.jpg";
---
<section id="about" class="bg-cream py-14 md:py-20">
  <div class="container grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[360px_1fr] md:gap-12 items-center">
    <!-- Photo -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] bg-sage/30">
      <img
        src={profile.src}
        alt="Dominique Newman, LCSW"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        width="720"
        height="720"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Copy -->
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-deep text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold mb-3">
        Meet Dominique Newman, LCSW
      </h2>
      <p class="mb-3">
        <em>Short welcoming intro (placeholder).</em> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur
        adipiscing elit. Morbi posuere sapien vitae sem feugiat, vel luctus nibh iaculis.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-3">
        Drawing from evidence-based approaches including CBT and mindfulness, Dominique provides a calm,
        collaborative space for growth and healing. Placeholder copy for 2–3 sentences to mirror
        Psychology Today / Alma tone.
      </p>
      <p class="text-deep/90">
        Individuals &amp; couples • Trauma • Anxiety • Depression • Life transitions
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- subtle divider -->
  <div class="container mt-12 md:mt-16">
    <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-deep/25 to-transparent"></div>
  </div>
</section>
